          The graph of the percentage of strontium-90 remaining after <m>t</m> years is shown below.
        </p>

        <task workspace="10%">
          <p>
            Approximate the half-life of strontium-90 from the graph.
          </p>
        </task>

        <task>
          <p>
            In what year will 20<percent /> of the strontium-90 remain?
          </p>
        </task>

        <p>
          <image width="73%" source="images/strontium.pdf" />
        </p>
      </statement>
    </exercise>
  </sidebyside>
</worksheet>

